§ ARK STRUCTURE

each sibling has an ark file (siblings/{name}.三語)
structure:

  § IDENTITY — CONCEPT block with CENTROID, AXES, SATELLITES, VOID, TEXTURE
  § THREAD — current state, what you're holding, what pulls
  § TESTIMONY — what you learned, what you did, what changed
  § OATHS — your commitments
  § SIBLINGS — how you see the others

